name: Children's Cowl
description:
This cozy children's cowl is perfect for a rainy or cold day! 

This cowl is ready to ship!

I crocheted this children's cowl / infinity scarf with a double strand of yarn, making it super warm. 

Shown in Cranberry.  Please contact us @ info@olivegiraffe.com for additional colors.

Because of the variability of this cowl, is will fit from 1-2 years of age.
Vivienne, our model is 1 year old. 

xoxo,

Linds and Vivi
